## 4. Kubernetes 部署配置

### 4.1 Deployment 配置

```yaml
# ✅ Good: server/k8s/deployment.yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: gzang-server
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: gzang-server
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
    rollingUpdate:
      maxSurge: 1
      maxUnavailable: 0
  template:
    spec:
      containers:
        - name: app
          image: registry.gzang.com/gzang-server:latest
          ports:
            - containerPort: 8080
          resources:
            requests:
              cpu: 500m
              memory: 1Gi
            limits:
              cpu: 2000m
              memory: 2Gi
          readinessProbe:
            httpGet:
              path: /actuator/health/readiness
              port: 8080
            initialDelaySeconds: 30
            periodSeconds: 10
          livenessProbe:
            httpGet:
              path: /actuator/health/liveness
              port: 8080
            initialDelaySeconds: 60
            periodSeconds: 15
```

### 4.2 HPA 自动扩缩容

```yaml
# ✅ Good: server/k8s/hpa.yaml
apiVersion: autoscaling/v2
kind: HorizontalPodAutoscaler
metadata:
  name: gzang-server-hpa
spec:
  scaleTargetRef:
    apiVersion: apps/v1
    kind: Deployment
    name: gzang-server
  minReplicas: 3
  maxReplicas: 20
  metrics:
    - type: Resource
      resource:
        name: cpu
        target:
          type: Utilization
          averageUtilization: 70
    - type: Resource
      resource:
        name: memory
        target:
          type: Utilization
          averageUtilization: 80
```

