## 6. 数据库备份

```yaml
# ✅ Good: 每日全量备份 CronJob
apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: mysql-backup
  namespace: production
spec:
  schedule: "0 2 * * *"
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 7
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
            - name: backup
              image: mysql:8.0
              command:
                - /bin/bash
                - -c
                - |
                  mysqldump -h$MYSQL_HOST -uroot -p$MYSQL_PASSWORD \
                    --single-transaction --routines --triggers \
                    --all-databases \
                    | gzip > /backup/full-backup-$(date +%Y%m%d).sql.gz
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
```

